location.n.01.defn: a point or extent in space

placement.n.03.defn: the act of putting something in a certain place

expl: he got a good fix on the target
localization.n.01.defn: a determination of the place where something is

expl: they shot the film on location in Nevada
location.n.04.defn: a workplace away from a studio at which some or all of a movie may be made

expl: what type of sculpture do you prefer?
type.n.01.defn: a subdivision of a particular kind of thing

character.n.05.defn: a person of a specified kind (usually with many eccentricities)

type.n.03.defn: (biology) the taxonomic group whose characteristics are used to define the next higher taxon

expl: small type is hard to read
the word `element' contains five different types of character
type.n.05.defn: all of the tokens of the same symbol

expl: he dropped a case of type, so they made him pick them up
type.n.06.defn: a small metal block bearing a raised character on one end; produces a printed character when inked and pressed on paper
